---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import ProcessStep from '../components/ProcessStep.astro';
import BenefitCard from '../components/BenefitCard.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Office Furniture Installation & Design | My Furniture Installer"
  description="Professional furniture installers and designers ready when you need them. Installation, layout planning, and coordination. Serving Washington DC, Northern Virginia, and Maryland."
>
  <Hero
    badge="Professional Installation & Design"
    title="Don't Worry, I Got A Guy"
    subtitle="If you already have office furniture—or you're planning to reuse or reconfigure it—you've got a guy to handle the installation so everything fits and works the way it should."
    primaryCta={{ text: "Get Connected", href: "/contact" }}
    secondaryCta={{ text: "How It Works", href: "/services" }}
    image="/images/hero.webp"
  />

  <section class="section furniture-challenge-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="challenge-content">
        <h2>Buying Office Furniture Is Easy. Making It Work Is Not.</h2>
        <p class="challenge-intro">Many businesses purchase used cubicles, acquire furniture from office liquidations, or already have systems in place. The furniture itself is often perfectly good. The challenge comes next.</p>
        <div class="challenge-points">
          <div class="challenge-point">
            <span class="challenge-icon">&#9633;</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Layout planning</strong>
              <p>How do you configure 40 cubicle panels to fit your floor plan?</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="challenge-point">
            <span class="challenge-icon">&#8644;</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Delivery coordination</strong>
              <p>Who receives, stages, and moves heavy furniture components?</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="challenge-point">
            <span class="challenge-icon">&#128295;</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Professional installation</strong>
              <p>Cubicles and modular systems require experienced installers to assemble correctly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="challenge-solution">This is exactly where we help. We handle the planning, coordination, and installation so your furniture actually works in your space.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section used-furniture-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="used-furniture-content">
        <div class="used-furniture-text">
          <h2>Already Have Furniture or Planning to Buy Used?</h2>
          <ul class="used-furniture-list">
            <li>Bought used cubicles but not sure how to set them up?</li>
            <li>Trying to reuse your existing office furniture?</li>
            <li>Unsure how to make everything fit your space?</li>
          </ul>
          <p>If you already have office furniture—or you're planning to reuse or reconfigure it—you've got a guy to handle the installation so everything fits and works the way it should.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Help With Your Setup</a>
        </div>
        <div class="used-furniture-visual">
          <img src="/images/process.webp" alt="Office furniture installation process" class="process-image" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section independent-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="independent-content">
        <span class="independent-badge">Flexible & Professional</span>
        <h2>Installation Experts On Your Side</h2>
        <p class="independent-intro">Whether you're working with a dealer, buying used, or reconfiguring what you have—we're the installation and design experts you can count on. One call, and you've got a guy.</p>
        <div class="independent-points">
          <div class="independent-point">
            <span class="check-icon">&#10003;</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Professional installation</strong>
              <p>Experienced installers certified in all major furniture systems. We do this every day.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="independent-point">
            <span class="check-icon">&#10003;</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Simple design services</strong>
              <p>Need a layout plan? We provide straightforward design services to make your space work.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="independent-point">
            <span class="check-icon">&#10003;</span>
            <div>
              <strong>Works with any situation</strong>
              <p>New furniture, used furniture, existing systems—we handle it all with the same expertise.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section problem-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>The Problem With New Office Furniture</h2>
        <p>Many companies face costly decisions when their office layout needs to change.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-grid">
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="problem-icon">&#36;</div>
          <h3>Expensive Quotes</h3>
          <p>New furniture systems cost $3,000-$8,000 per workstation. A 50-cubicle office can easily exceed $200,000.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="problem-icon">&#128203;</div>
          <h3>Untapped Value</h3>
          <p>Like cars, office furniture loses most of its value in year one—but not its usefulness. Your existing systems have decades of life left.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="problem-card">
          <div class="problem-icon">&#10067;</div>
          <h3>No Clear Path</h3>
          <p>Facilities managers know something can be done, but don't know where to start or who to call.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section solution-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="solution-content">
        <div class="solution-text">
          <span class="solution-badge">The Better Way</span>
          <h2>Reuse What You Have. Save Thousands.</h2>
          <p>Most offices only need a few new parts and pieces—not entirely new furniture. We reconfigure what you have, source only what's missing, and keep perfectly good furniture out of the landfill.</p>
          <ul class="solution-list">
            <li>
              <span class="check-icon">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Full inventory of your existing furniture assets</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="check-icon">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Custom layout design based on your needs</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="check-icon">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Professional disassembly and reinstallation</span>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="check-icon">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Minimal disruption to your operations</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get a Free Office Plan</a>
        </div>
        <div class="solution-visual">
          <img src="/images/solution.webp" alt="Office cubicle workstations" class="solution-image" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section process-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p>A straightforward process to get your office space working.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-grid process-grid-4">
        <ProcessStep
          number="1"
          title="Project Review"
          description="We assess your furniture inventory, understand your space requirements, and review your floor plan and goals."
        />
        <ProcessStep
          number="2"
          title="Layout & Reconfiguration Planning"
          description="Our team designs an optimized layout that maximizes your existing or newly acquired furniture."
        />
        <ProcessStep
          number="3"
          title="Installation Coordination"
          description="We coordinate delivery, staging, and professional installation with minimal disruption to your operations."
        />
        <ProcessStep
          number="4"
          title="Completed Workspace"
          description="Your office is ready to use with furniture properly configured, connected, and fully functional."
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section benefits-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Why Companies Choose Us</h2>
        <p>Real benefits that impact your bottom line and operations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <BenefitCard
          icon="&#128176;"
          title="Significant Cost Savings"
          description="Save 50-60% compared to purchasing new furniture systems. Typical projects save $50,000-$150,000."
          stat="50-60%"
          statLabel="average savings"
        />
        <BenefitCard
          icon="&#9201;"
          title="Faster Turnaround"
          description="No waiting for new furniture orders. Most projects complete in days, not weeks or months."
          stat="5-10"
          statLabel="day average project"
        />
        <BenefitCard
          icon="&#9851;"
          title="The Smartest Green Choice"
          description="Manufacturers invest millions in solar panels and green certifications—but nothing beats using furniture for its full lifespan before it hits a landfill."
        />
        <BenefitCard
          icon="&#128736;"
          title="Expert Installation"
          description="Our certified installers have years of experience with all major furniture systems."
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    title="Ready to Have Your Own Guy?"
    description="Connect with professional installers and designers who handle the hard part—so your office just works."
    buttonText="Get Connected"
    buttonHref="/contact"
  />

  <section class="section areas-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Serving the Greater DC Area</h2>
        <p>Local experts providing office furniture services throughout the region.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a href="/locations#dc" class="area-card">
          <h3>Washington DC</h3>
          <p>Downtown, Capitol Hill, Georgetown, Navy Yard, and all DC neighborhoods.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/locations#virginia" class="area-card">
          <h3>Northern Virginia</h3>
          <p>Arlington, Tysons, Fairfax, Alexandria, Reston, and surrounding areas.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/locations#maryland" class="area-card">
          <h3>Maryland</h3>
          <p>Bethesda, Silver Spring, Rockville, College Park, and Montgomery County.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    variant="light"
    title="Questions? Let's Talk."
    description="Not sure what you need? We'll help you figure it out—no sales pitch, no product pushing."
    buttonText="Contact Us"
    buttonHref="/contact"
  />
</Layout>

<style>
  .furniture-challenge-section {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
  }

  .challenge-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .challenge-content h2 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
  }

  .challenge-intro {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .challenge-points {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .challenge-point {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }

  .challenge-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }

  .challenge-point strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .challenge-point p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .challenge-solution {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    text-align: left;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .used-furniture-section {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .used-furniture-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .used-furniture-text h2 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .used-furniture-list {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .used-furniture-list li {
    color: var(--color-text);
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
  }

  .used-furniture-list li::before {
    content: "•";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .used-furniture-text > p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .used-furniture-visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .process-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .independent-section {
    background: var(--color-bg-light);
  }

  .independent-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .independent-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.375rem 0.875rem;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .independent-content h2 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .independent-intro {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .independent-points {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .independent-point {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .independent-point .check-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background: #ecfdf5;
    color: var(--color-success);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
  }

  .independent-point strong {
    display: block;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .independent-point p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .problem-section {
    background: var(--color-bg-light);
  }

  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .problem-card {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }

  .problem-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: #fef2f2;
    color: var(--color-error);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
  }

  .problem-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .problem-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .solution-section {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .solution-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .solution-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.375rem 0.875rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 50px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .solution-text h2 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .solution-text > p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .solution-list {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .solution-list li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .check-icon {
    color: var(--color-success);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .solution-visual {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .solution-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .process-section {
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
  }

  .process-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .process-grid-4 {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  }

  .benefits-section {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .areas-section {
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .areas-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .area-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-light);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .area-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .area-card h3 {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .area-card p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .challenge-points {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    }

    .used-furniture-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .used-furniture-visual {
      order: -1;
    }

    .problem-grid,
    .process-grid,
    .process-grid-4,
    .areas-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .solution-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .solution-visual {
      order: -1;
    }

    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .visual-card {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .visual-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
    }

    .visual-box {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .visual-plus,
    .visual-equals {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
